<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10437996>
    dc:description "FIGURE 55. Collected specimens (A−C), and distribution in southeastern Brazil and adjacent areas (D−F). Gerromorpha, Veliidae. A. Stridulivelia astralis, micropterous male from Ecoporanga, Espírito Santo (–18.3444, –40.8792). B. Stridulivelia quadrispinosa, micropterous male from Ecoporanga, Espírito Santo (–18.3578, –40.8828). C. Stridulivelia tersa, micropterous male from Sooretama, Espírito Santo (−19.0269, −40.2276). Stars indicate new records; circles indicate previous records. Scale bars: 1 mm (A, B), 2 mm (C)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10437996/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

